<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="30Nov1934"><font color="red">30 November 1934</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from J. Ralph Pinker to Paul L&eacute;on): I understand that the next issue of <i>transition</i> is going to come out before very long &hellip; Faber and Faber very much hope &hellip; they may be allowed to reissue the new fragment in separate form, as with Anna Livia and the others. </div>
